high_descs: Move forward, turn left after the sink to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up the bread across the counter to the left.
Turn around, bring the bread to the fridge on the left.
Chill the bread in the fridge.
Bring the chilled bread to the counter right of the fridge.
Put the bread on the counter right of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread on the counter, right of the fridge.

high_descs: walk forwards to the end of the kitchen island counter on your left, then turn left to face it
grab the bread off of the kitchen island counter
turn around and walk to the front of the fridge on the left
place the bread inside of the fridge to cool down, then take it back out again
turn left and walk over to the kitchen counter on the left to the left of the stove
place the bread down on the kitchen counter to the right of the toaster
anns.task_desc: place the cooled bread down on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Move to the end of the island on your left.
Pick up the loaf of bread closest to the sink.
Turn around and move to the front of the fridge.
Put the loaf of bread on the second shelf of the fridge for a few minutes and then remove it.
Move a few steps to the counter on your right.
Set the loaf of bread down on the counter above the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled loaf of bread on the counter above the dishwasher.
